"Too Good To Be Forgotten" is a song originally by The Chi-Lites in 1974 reaching no. 10 in the UK Singles chart, however it was a bigger hit for Amazulu in 1986 from their album Amazulu. It reached no. 5 on the UK Singles chart, making it their highest charting & only top 10 single on that chart. The song has also been covered by John Holt
